 shirt, her jeans. They let each item drop to the floor, where it remained, a discarded shell. Her body was lean and unformed, his solid and defined by adulthood.\n\nHe lay her on the bed, the coverlet cool beneath her back. He positioned himself over her, his arms holding himself up. He looked at her face, at the expectation and the lack of fear in her eyes. He kissed her, a hard, direct press of lips. It wasn't gentle; it was an act of consumption.\n\nHis hands moved over her body, learning the planes of her stomach, the curve of her hip. His mouth followed the path his hands had taken, his tongue tracing circuits on her skin that made her muscles tense. When his head was between her thighs, he didn't tease or wors", "embedding": [-0.10965683311223984, 0.06996489316225052, -0.003638901049271226, 0.06251637637615204, 0.07447367161512375, 0.017272671684622765, 0.08554177731275558, 0.0654458999633789, -0.014952053315937519, -0.011753118596971035, 0.05389108136296272, 0.009077063761651516, -0.029111159965395927, 0.07570699602365494, 0.0463695153594017, 0.005776164587587118, 0.02288036234676838, 0.011833006516098976, -0.044615451246500015, 0.02757399156689644, 0.007191252429038286, 0.044482696801424026, 0.07042370736598969, -0.015061930753290653, 0.026058074086904526, 0.017036743462085724, -0.01154372002929449, 0.011838233098387718, -0.09731573611497879, 0.058885637670755386, -0.08505424112081528, 0.003360862610861659, 0.07217897474765778, 0.0796518623828888, -0.0808800607919693, 0.07186508178710938, 0.01644798368215561, 0.07968045771121979, 0.11126799136400223, -0.023084301501512527, -0.033929672092199326, -0.010755316354334354, -0.00404725968837738, 0.04359632357954979, 0.013198711909353733, -0.015531769022345543, 0.0028829826042056084, -0.004552418366074562, 0.033831119537353516, -0.031636793166399, -0.07911781966686249, -0.004444577731192112, -0.003106515621766448, -0.022154798731207848, -0.0364384725689888, 0.013542604632675648, 0.02644485980272293, 0.022220712155